i tried setting 
echo 60 > /sys/module/usbhid/parameters/mousepoll
or changing the kernel boot parameter usbhid.mousepoll, but it doesn't
help.
i just fired up a knoppix cd with 2.6.11 kernel and the mouse works
fine there so there must be something wrong with my setup..??
tx for any hints,
